## Transitions & Interactions

- **Standard**: `all 0.2s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1)`
- **Fast**: `0.15s ease`
- **Hover lift (cards)**: `transform: translateY(-2px)` with elevated shadow
- **Hover lift (buttons)**: `transform: translateY(-1px)` with enhanced shadow
- **Active press**: `transform: translateY(0)` with reduced shadow
- **Animations**: `slideIn` (drawers), `fadeIn` (overlays), `pulse-badge` (notifications)

## Component Patterns

### Buttons
- **Primary** (`.btn-primary`): Blue gradient bg, white text, `border-radius: 0.5rem`, hover lift
- **Secondary** (`.btn-secondary`): White bg, subtle border, muted text
- **Ghost** (`.btn-ghost`): Transparent bg, light border
- **Swap CTA** (`.btn-swap`): Blue gradient, `border-radius: 0.625rem`, inline-flex with arrow icon
- **Landing primary** (`.lp-btn-primary`): Larger padding `0.7rem 1.4rem`, `border-radius: 0.75rem`

### Cards
- White background, `border-radius: 1.25rem`, `border: 2px solid rgba(226, 232, 240, 0.6)`
- Hover: lift + blue border tint + elevated shadow
- Deal variant: blue-tinted border + light blue gradient bg
- Completed variant: green-tinted border + light green gradient bg

### Badges & Pills
- `border-radius: 999px`, tiny padding `0.3rem 0.75rem`
- Urgent: red gradient bg + red text + pulse animation
- Normal: light gray bg + muted text
- Status pills use gradient backgrounds matching semantic colors

### Inputs
- `border-radius: 0.875rem`, `border: 1.5px solid rgba(226, 232, 240, 0.8)`
- Focus: blue border `rgba(96, 165, 250, 0.8)` + blue ring `0 0 0 4px rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.08)`
- Hover (unfocused): slightly darker border

### Banners
- `border-radius: 1.25rem`, prominent padding `1.5rem 1.75rem`
- Savings banner: Primary blue gradient bg, white text, star icon
- Warning: amber gradient bg, dark amber text
- Error: red gradient bg, dark red text

### Skeleton Loaders
- `border-radius: 0.35rem`
- Animated gradient: `#F3F4F6 → #E5E7EB → #F3F4F6`
- Animation: `background-size: 200% 100%` sliding

## Responsive Breakpoints

- **Mobile**: `max-width: 640px` — single-column layouts, full-width buttons, hidden decorative elements
- **Tablet**: `max-width: 960px` — simplified grids, stacked layouts

## Icons

- Inline SVGs only (no icon library)
- Stroke-based: `strokeWidth: 1.5`, `strokeLinecap: "round"`, `strokeLinejoin: "round"`
- Sizes: `12px` (badges), `16px` (inline), `20px` (buttons/nav), `24px` (cards), `48px` (empty states)
- Color inherits from parent via `stroke="currentColor"` or explicit color
